Package: simulateGP
Title: Functions for simulating genotype-phenotype relationships
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: c(
	person("Gibran", "Hemani", email = "explodecomputer@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
	person("John", "Ferguson", email = "john.ferguson@nuigalway.ie", role = c("aut")))
Description: Functions for simulating SNP effects on phenotypes. Functions for
    simulating disease risk on probability and liability scales. Simulations to
    quickly obtain estimates of effect sizes for simulated genotype-phenotypes.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
